941
01:21:32.392 --> 01:21:35.979
<i>What I done that
God hates me so?</i>

942
01:21:42.068 --> 01:21:44.237
It's that godless lot.

943
01:21:46.156 --> 01:21:48.033
They brought this on me.

944
01:21:48.158 --> 01:21:50.410
I bring them God's
word and heathens

945
