in three weeks' time.

973
01:24:29.486 --> 01:24:31.738
I'll hold out your name to him.

974
01:24:32.072 --> 01:24:34.491
What you earn is yours to keep.

975
01:24:35.241 --> 01:24:36.326
Yes, sir.

976
01:24:36.993 --> 01:24:38.244
Mind yourself, Platt.

977
