1027
01:29:51.224 --> 01:29:52.559
I did not know, sir.

1028
01:29:52.726 --> 01:29:54.310
Not "sir."

1029
01:29:55.061 --> 01:29:56.730
Just "Armsby."

1030
01:29:57.605 --> 01:29:59.733
I'm not owed more than
any other in the field.

1031
01:30:00.066 --> 01:30:03.069
